{
  "text": "The effect of the relative intakes of the 2 types of polyunsaturated fat on the relative tissue concentrations of the progenitors of the n\u04803 and n\u04806 eicosanoids has been well elucidated. An empirical formula has been derived that predicts the relative proportions of the 2 progenitors by using only dietary fat composition [CITATION_1] . The ratio of n\u04803 to n\u04806 fatty acids is a component 2 The statistical significance of the pooled estimate for the medians of nutrients as continuous variables. [CITATION_2] The statistical significance of the test for between-study heterogeneity in the continuous median variables used for testing trends.",
